Deborah Oluwaseun Odeyemi (amụrụ na mkpụrụ ụbochị iri abụọ na-otu n'ọnwa Febụwarị na-afọ 1995) bụ onye Naijiria na-agba ọsọ nke na-agba 100 mita, 200 mita, 4 x 100 mita na sprint medley relay. O sonyere na asọmpi 4 × 100 mita relay na-afọ 2015 World Championships na Athletics na Beijing, China.
Odeyemi nwalere na ọ nwere metenolone anabolic steroid na sample anakọtara na Nigerian Championship na mkpụrụ ụbọchị iri atọ n'ọnwa Julaị na-afọ 2015
A kagbuola nsonaazụ ya site na 2015 World Championships in Athletics ma nye ya mmachibido iwu afọ anọ site na egwuregwu.
